title: The Parallel (2014)
overview: Pregnant Emmy is drugged by her boyfriend and taken to an illegal abortion clinic, but the ordeal makes her sterile. One day she decides to adopt an orphan girl who always keeps a doll which turns out to be possessed.
storyline: A little girl witnesses the brutal murder of her mother during working hours in a Thailand store. Strange things begin to occur when she gets older, hence insinuating a curse is with her.
